channel.title: Smithsonian National Air and Space Museum
channel.description:
I plan on going there tomorrow, and am willing to take pictures of it's exhibits by request. I'm going to the one at the National Mall.
[url]https://www.nasm.si.edu/[/url]
I don't know if anyone will even want me to take a picture of anything for them, but figured I would offer. I'll dump all pictures that people request in here after I've uploaded them.

item.title: Smithsonian National Air and Space Museum
item.dc:creator: BahamutBBob
item.description:
Mont_Blanc:

If you got time :

Planes and stuff

The stuff you listed is in the other building, which is at Dulles Airport. I went to the one right off of The Mall in DC. I do want to go there again though, they have like, 10 shitloads of planes.

super lurker:

touch the moon rock at the entrance for me

I would have, but it wasn’t there. The display for it was there, but the rock itself was not.

Let’s see if this works. I put the pictures in my SkyDrive, because it’s a lot quicker to go through my phone and say “Upload to SkyDrive” than it is to put them all on imageshack.

Link.

There is also a picture of my dog in there that I took yesterday to test the whole thing out.

Also, when I took the pic of the SR-71 model, there were some kids that were all “Woah, it’s just like in Black Ops!” I wanted to facepalm. Because they looked about 12.
